n class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>styles<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>button<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\"> </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>now <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"etc\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> styles<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>active <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> styles<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>none<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> \n                        <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>etc<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n                        Etc.\n                    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n                </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\n                </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>styles<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>workList<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n                    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token function\">dataDraw</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>workData<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> now<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n                </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n\n            </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Dev14_001_Change\"\n        title=\"Dev14_001_Change\"\n        src=\"/static/88955e877fcba479166aaa11c787dbbb/37523/Dev14_001_Change.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/88955e877fcba479166aaa11c787dbbb/e9ff0/Dev14_001_Change.png 180w,\n/static/88955e877fcba479166aaa11c787dbbb/f21e7/Dev14_001_Change.png 360w,\n/static/88955e877fcba479166aaa11c787dbbb/37523/Dev14_001_Change.png 720w,\n/static/88955e877fcba479166aaa11c787dbbb/302a4/Dev14_001_Change.png 1080w,\n/static/88955e877fcba479166aaa11c787dbbb/c1bea/Dev14_001_Change.png 1388w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4-%EB%B6%84%EB%A5%98\">기존 분류</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EB%B6%84%EB%A5%98-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD\">분류 변경</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\">코드 수정</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"포트폴리오 작업물 분류 태그를 수정합니다. 기존에 작업물들을 분류하기 애매했던 부분을 조금 더 명확히 수정했습니다. 기존 분류 기존에는 “Tech - Art - Documents” 로 나누어져있는 상황이었습니다.\n허나 취업을 메인으로 생각했을 때, 분류를 “게임과 다른 분야” 로 나누는 것이 맞다고 생각합니다. 다만, 작업물들이 전체적으로 게임 쪽이 아닌 미디어아트와 같은 분야.\n혹은 그냥 게임 엔진을 사용한 분야이기에 분류하기 애매했습니다. 게임으로 분야를 한정한다면, 20년 1인 개발 게임이 가장 마지막이기에 약간 애매한 상황입니다.\n개인 작업물들, 토이 프로젝트(라고 할 것도 없는 진짜 연습한 것들…)을 넣는다고 해도 분량이 애매합니다. 분류 변경 상기한 이유로 작업물 분류를 다음과 같이 재설정합니다. ALL Unreal Engine 3D Graphics ETC 기존과 사실 상 크게 다른 점은 없습니다.\n작업물들의 특성상 기존 Tech 분류를 Unreal engine으로 분야…","frontmatter":{"date":"December 04, 2024","title":"DEV 14. 태그 수정","categories":"PORTFOLIO","author":"JunHyeong Moon","emoji":""},"fields":{"slug":"/Portfolio/PortfolioDev_014/"}},"next":{"id":"3f8c7504-0f69-505c-90f5-2137a8428ad4","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>기존 svg 파일을 통해 관리하던 아이콘들을<br>\nmui를 통해 조금 더 수월하게 수정/관리 할 수 있도록 변경합니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"mui\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mui\" aria-label=\"mui permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>mui</h2>\n<p>기존 사용하던 아이콘들은 직접 svg 파일을 이용하여 사용했습니다.<br>\n다만 그 부분에서 아이콘들이 통일되지 않은 느낌도 있었고, 색상 전환이 필요한 경우와 크기 조절이 필요한 경우에 귀찮게 된다는 단점이 있었습니다.</p>\n<p>그러던 중, 블로그 디자인을 수정하다가 블로그 템플릿에 사용된 mui를 발견했습니다.<br>\nmui는 구글의 머티리얼 디자인을 기반으로 한 리액트 UI 컴포넌트 라이브러리로, 일관된 디자인과 사용성을 보장한다고 합니다. <a href=\"https://f-lab.kr/insight/starting-frontend-development-with-nextjs-and-mui\">(정보 사이트)</a><br>\n특히 아이콘에서 <a href=\"https://mui.com/material-ui/material-icons/\">이렇게 찾을 수 있게 정리 된 도큐멘트</a>가 있어서 꽤나 유용하게 쓸 수 있을 것 같습니다.</p>\n<p>아이콘 이외에도 다양한 부분들이 템플릿처럼 라이브러리화되어있어 조금 살펴보니, 아이콘 이외에도 툴팁, 슬라이더등 수많은 부분에 대한 내용들이 담겨있었습니다.<br>\n사용도 꽤 간편하고, 디자인도 깔끔하고, 문서화도 잘되어있어서인지 이렇게 라이브러리를 많이 사용하는 것 같습니다.</p>\n<p>그럼 얼른 써봐야겠죠.<br>\n일단 저는 아이콘에만 사용해보도록 하겠습니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"mui-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mui-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"mui 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>mui 설치</h2>\n<p>공식 문서에서 icons 사용에 대한 설치 방법부터 사용법까지 안내해주고 있습니다.<br>\n해당 내용을 바탕으로 설치를 진행했습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"git\"><pre class=\"language-git\"><code class=\"language-git\">npm install @mui/icons-material @mui/material @emotion/styled @emotion/react</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.55555555555556%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Dev13_001_Install\"\n        title=\"Dev13_001_Install\"\n        src=\"/static/bdaaea703ec299fe8b22b834704f74c2/37523/Dev13_001_Install.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bdaaea703ec299fe8b22b834704f74c2/e9ff0/Dev13_001_Install.png 180w,\n/static/bdaaea703ec299fe8b22b834704f74c2/f21e7/Dev13_001_Install.png 360w,\n/static/bdaaea703ec299fe8b22b834704f74c2/37523/Dev13_001_Install.png 720w,\n/static/bdaaea703ec299fe8b22b834704f74c2/f5209/Dev13_001_Install.png 1061w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"아이콘-수정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%95%84%EC%9D%B4%EC%BD%98-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"아이콘 수정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>아이콘 수정</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://mui.com/material-ui/material-icons/\">공식 문서</a> 에서 사용할 아이콘을 찾으면 아래 이미지와 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">import</code> 코드가 함께 보여집니다.<br>\n해당 코드를 복붙하여 사용해주겠습니다.</p>\n<p><em>FAB 메일 아이콘 수정을 바탕으로 작성합니다.</em></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Dev13_002_iconSearch\"\n        title=\"Dev13_002_iconSearch\"\n        src=\"/static/80dab0ccba6714007c2ddebd310323e8/37523/Dev13_002_iconSearch.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/80dab0ccba6714007c2ddebd310323e8/e9ff0/Dev13_002_iconSearch.png 180w,\n/static/80dab0ccba6714007c2ddebd310323e8/f21e7/Dev13_002_iconSearch.png 360w,\n/static/80dab0ccba6714007c2ddebd310323e8/37523/Dev13_002_iconSearch.png 720w,\n/static/80dab0ccba6714007c2ddebd310323e8/2e367/Dev13_002_iconSearch.png 1066w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>해당 코드를 <code class=\"language-text\">floatingBUtton.js</code> 컴포넌트 최상단에 작성해주겠습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// src/components/floatingButton/floatingButton.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> EmailIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/icons-material/Email'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">FloatingButton</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>기존 이미지를 이용해서 작성하던 부분을 임포트한 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;EmailIcon /></code>을 활용하는 것으로 바꾸겠습니다.<br>\n아이콘 스타일의 경우 <code class=\"language-text\">font-size</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">color</code> 기반으로 수정이 가능하여, 모듈 css에서 수정할 수 있도록 스타일 클래스를 지정해주었습니다. <code class=\"language-text\">font-size</code>의 경우 인라인으로 설정하였습니다.<br>\n추가로 label까지 작성하였습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token comment\">// src/components/floatingButton/floatingButton.js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> EmailIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/icons-material/Email'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// before</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Image</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/icons/Mail.svg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">26</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">26</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Mail<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Mail<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// after</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">EmailIcon</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">className</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>styles<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>icon<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">label</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Mail<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fontSzie</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>medium<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* src/components/floatingButton/floating.module.css */</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.icon</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #505050<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이와 같은 방식으로 수정을 진행합니다.<br>\nFAB, modalFAB, 프로필 “자기소개 더보기” 아이콘 모두 수정을 진행하였습니다.</p>\n<p>아래는 수정 완료된 모습입니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 42.77777777777778%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Dev13_003_ProfileIcon\"\n        title=\"Dev13_003_ProfileIcon\"\n        src=\"/static/06f13de83e366bbfcee3e4a0b554bed5/37523/Dev13_003_ProfileIcon.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/06f13de83e366bbfcee3e4a0b554bed5/e9ff0/Dev13_003_ProfileIcon.png 180w,\n/static/06f13de83e366bbfcee3e4a0b554bed5/f21e7/Dev13_003_ProfileIcon.png 360w,\n/static/06f13de83e366bbfcee3e4a0b554bed5/37523/Dev13_003_ProfileIcon.png 720w,\n/static/06f13de83e366bbfcee3e4a0b554bed5/302a4/Dev13_003_ProfileIcon.png 1080w,\n/static/06f13de83e366bbfcee3e4a0b554bed5/061c7/Dev13_003_ProfileIcon.png 1216w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 458px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Dev13_004_FabIcon\"\n        title=\"Dev13_004_FabIcon\"\n        src=\"/static/a61ac4dd7af4e71f15471dae97e12e22/f